      ],
      "message": "test: remove circular dependency between authproxy and util\n\nThere's a circular dependency between authproxy.py and util.py\ndue to which the former can't use the common utility functions\nand thus lazy imports are used as a workaround.\n\nThis patch moves the RPC related functions from util.py to\nrpc_util.py so that authproxy.py can use the utility functions\nfrom util.py in a standard fashion. There are already *_util\nmodules so this new one follows them.\n\nThe call sites of the moved functions had to be changed from\nutil.py to rpc_util.py, most of which are for the\nassert_raises_rpc_error function.",
